revision.text:
{{codepointer|Sound}}void '''A_Scream''' ()
{{doomwiki|A_Scream}}

==Usage==
Plays the actor's {{Property|DeathSound|death sound}} if it has one. If the actor has either the {{Flag|BOSS}} or {{Flag|FULLVOLDEATH}} flags, the sound is heard at full volume regardless of distance, otherwise it diminishes by distance. The sound is played on the ''voice'' [[Sound channels|channel]].

This function can be combined with {{c|[[A_NoBlocking]]}} using {{c|[[A_ScreamAndUnblock]]}}.

==Examples==
This is the Death state sequence of {{Class|DoomImp|Doom's Imp}}.
 Death:
     TROO I 8;
     TROO J 8 [[A_Scream]];
     TROO K 6;
     TROO L 6 [[A_NoBlocking]];
     TROO M -1;
     Stop;
